author: kanhiyachauhan
title: Amazing Facts About India
body:
India is the only country, in which the population of the whole world is settled. In India, every society or every class of people live together. The history of this country is quite old and there is a lot of information that everybody does not know. We are giving some Amazing Facts About India. Which you would liked -

  1. India is the world's oldest and most developed civilization country.
  2. By the 17th Century, India was the richest country in the world.
  3. India is a country which has never attacked any country in history.
  4. According to the International Institute of Strategic Studies, India has the largest army after China. America at number three.
  5. India is the only country in the world, where 31-42% of the population is vegetarian.
  6. There are more than 3,00,000 mosques in India, not so much in any Muslim country.
  7. "0" was invented by Aryabhata. Who was an Indian.
  8. Every 12 years, a Kumbh fair is organized in India, where people from all religions are gathered, in this sense this is the world's largest fair.
  9. Tea is the national drink of India.
  10. India's name has been taken from the river Indus.
  11. The Indus Valley civilization is considered to be the oldest civilization in the world.
  12. In terms of Muslim population, India is at number three.
  13. India is the second largest English speaking country after the US in the world.
  14. India is the seventh (7th) largest country in the world. India has 3,287,263 square kilometers of land. But only 9.6% is water on land.
  15. India is the world's largest arms importer.
  16. The number of people born in India every year is more than that of Australia and other countries.
  17. India's Indira Gandhi Airport is the second largest and best airport in the world.
  18. Microprocessor Pentium Chip Indian-origin scientist Vinod Dham was invented.
  19. Did you know that India was an island about 100 million years ago.
  20. KFC has introduced a vegetarian menu just for India.
  21. India is the world's largest producer of milk.
  22. After the United States and Britain, India is the only country whose highest guinness is the world record.
  23. Chess is the oldest game in the world, which was invented in India only in the 6th century AD.
  24. Do you know the shampoo was discovered in India itself. In India shampoo was made from herbs. Shampoo word is taken from the Sanskrit language "champu", which means "massage"
  25. Diamond was first searched in India.
  26. India is the world's largest film producer.
  27. The cricket pitch of Himachal Pradesh is the world's highest pitch. It has been constructed 2444 meters above sea level.
  28. India has only discovered the value of Pi.
  29. India is also one of the three nations to create a supercomputer. (The second two is US and Japan.)
  30. Plastic surgery has also been discovered in India.
  31. Do you know, Ravindranath Tagore has written the national anthem of India as well as the national anthem "Amar Sonar Bangla" of Bangladesh.
  32. India's railway department is the highest job giving department in the world.
  33. Today, India's economy is the world's third largest economy.
  34. Martial arts also came first in India.
  35. Pizza Hut opened its first vegetarian restaurant in India.
  36. Located in Lucknow, "City Montessori School" is the world's largest school, with approximately 52,000 students and 1050 class rooms.

Thank You For Reading!



Posted from my blog with SteemPress : http://www.uniqueinspirationworld.com/amazing-facts-about-india/

author: rt-international
title: Millions of black holes bouncing around galaxy after being booted at birth, study finds
body:
One of the leading theories about the origins of black holes suggests they come from gargantuan supernova explosions. New research suggests these blasts may be so powerful, they literally kick black holes around the galaxy.
If proven correct, this would mean that, throughout the galaxy and indeed the wider universe, there are likely millions of black holes bouncing around at fantastically high speeds of 70km/s (43 miles per second). 

“This [work](https://arxiv.org/abs/1908.07199) basically talks about the first observational evidence that you can actually see black holes moving with high velocities in the galaxy and associate it to the kick the black hole system received at birth,” astronomer Pikky Atri of Curtin University and the International Centre for Radio Astronomy Research (ICRAR) said. 

The study concentrated on 16 black holes in binary star systems as the gravitational force of a black hole is so strong that we can’t detect any electromagnetic radiation emanating from it unless we catch it feeding on something, like its binary partner, for example.

![5d68fd2bdda4c876078b460f.jpg](https://cdn.steemitimages.com/DQmQhxiyzfwTSHGVP3jgXcirRh8ubgtnZ79K5saxsYem9gt/5d68fd2bdda4c876078b460f.jpg)
*Illustration: © Garik Barseghyan from Pixabay*

As the black hole consumes its stellar sibling, the matter being swallowed up emits powerful X-rays and radio waves, allowing Earth-bound scientists a chance to home in on them. 

With the ability to track black holes, they began retracing their movements by reverse-engineering their velocities to understand where, and how, they originated, either by collapsing in on themselves without a supernova explosion or with a tremendous punt in a similar way as to what happens when neutron stars die. 

Neutron stars experience what is known as a Blaauw kick or a natal kick, which sends them flying across the stars, so researchers wanted to determine whether the same could be true for black holes. They found that 75 percent of the black holes studied did indeed receive a swift kick up the backside the moment they were born.

With approximately 10 million black holes estimated to be in the Milky Way, that means there are potentially 7.5 million black holes ricocheting through the stars. 

We needn’t worry about the Earth getting smashed in the face by an errant cosmic free kick, however. 

“The closest black hole, we think it’s two kiloparsecs away [6,523 light-years],” Atri said.

“It’s very, very far away. So there’s no chance that we’re getting sucked up by any black hole any time soon.”

[MORE ON RT](https://www.rt.com/news/467616-millions-black-holes-bouncing-around/)
root_title: Millions of black holes bouncing around galaxy after being booted at birth, study finds

author: sinochip
title: One General - dinner with friends and family
body:
![title_image](https://static.tasteem.io/uploads/759/post/41834/content_4472060b-735b-47f8-9a5e-39e0bf7de4bf.jpeg)
This is fast becoming my favourite restaurant to meet up with friends. It's called One and the Chinese chacracter behind it means General, so I'm going to call it One General. ![DSC_1914.JPG](https://static.tasteem.io/uploads/image/image/207995/4904178c-4b12-4c46-856f-b6220805ff42.jpeg) I don't know how long this place has been opened as my friend told me about it about six months ago, and she's been a few times. I have a feeling it used to be another type of restuarant, or maybe a cafe as the decor doesn't seem to suit the type of food they serve. If you look at the decor, its very modern, and even has a British red phone box. If I didn't know, I'd think it serves western food. ![DSC_1913.JPG](https://static.tasteem.io/uploads/image/image/207996/4904178c-4b12-4c46-856f-b6220805ff42.jpeg) ![DSC_1911.JPG](https://static.tasteem.io/uploads/image/image/207997/4904178c-4b12-4c46-856f-b6220805ff42.jpeg) The counter is very modern and sleek, and white brick like tiles gives this young hippish look. ![DSC_1910.JPG](https://static.tasteem.io/uploads/image/image/207998/4904178c-4b12-4c46-856f-b6220805ff42.jpeg) One General actually serves hearthy traditional local Chinese food and is a great place for large groups like friends and family. You'll see what I mean when I show you the dishes. Starting from the starter, this is a spicy calamari and is served cold. It's got a fanatastic spicy kick, similar to the Thai spice. It's great as a starter. 8/10 ![DSC_1902.JPG](https://static.tasteem.io/uploads/image/image/207999/4904178c-4b12-4c46-856f-b6220805ff42.jpeg) Chicken wings are my favourite. It's the first time I've had it here. They were done very well, but nothing to wowed by, to be honest. 7/10 ![DSC_1906.JPG](https://static.tasteem.io/uploads/image/image/208003/4904178c-4b12-4c46-856f-b6220805ff42.jpeg) This is fresh bambooshoots with chicken. This is a great dish when its made with fresh bambooshoots, and has a great aroma. The chicken was stir fried just right and still very succelent. 8/10 ![DSC_1905.JPG](https://static.tasteem.io/uploads/image/image/208002/4904178c-4b12-4c46-856f-b6220805ff42.jpeg) This is pork with braised auberguine. Taiwanese cuisine often adds basil to their food taking the dishes to another level. 8/10 ![DSC_1904.JPG](https://static.tasteem.io/uploads/image/image/208001/4904178c-4b12-4c46-856f-b6220805ff42.jpeg) And finally, this is best dish of all. The is a pan of glass noodle in seafood broth which of course has seafood inside. There's also lots of other ingredients such as yam and tofu. It's served on a stove and cooks gently and the flavour of the soup intensifies as you eat. 10/10 for this. ![DSC_1903.JPG](https://static.tasteem.io/uploads/image/image/208000/4904178c-4b12-4c46-856f-b6220805ff42.jpeg) So you can see why this is my weekly choice for dinner with friends and family. --------------------- ### Restaurant Information
One General ![score](https://static.tasteem.io/images/2Crowns_en.png) [No. 460, Section 4, Wenxin Road, Beitun District, Taichung City, Taiwan 406](https://tasteem.io/post/41834#map) -----------------------------------------
[One General - dinner with friends and family](https://tasteem.io/post/41834) This post participated in the Tasteem contest [Your weekly choice ](https://tasteem.io/event/571)
[What is Tasteem?](https://tasteem.io/about) [![tasteem_banner.png](https://static.tasteem.io/images/tasteem_banner_en_v3.png)](https://tasteem.io)

title: 选错卡，输得很难看！...
body:
http://newappaz.oss-cn-hongkong.aliyuncs.com/wherein_images/post/20190802/95ae7d816fda47dc989c8fac1e0bb7c7.jpg



选错卡，输得很难看！

今天没抽到死亡系任务，来分析一下上面这次战斗。

选卡环节，我看到对方一直使用水系卡片对战，这场对战毫无悬念的又选了水系卡片。

我潜意识里就觉得如果水系卡片出战，大概率会以魔法做主攻。

这次我错了，我花了很大代价压制对方的魔法攻击，结果对方没用魔法卡片。

由于规则限制召唤师的能力，对方选择了两张具有潜行能力的卡片做主攻。

总结一下:下次在遇到这种规则下水系对手，一定要选用潜行或者瞄准功能的卡片。

来自于 [WhereIn Android] (http://www.wherein.io)

author: aldercysteem
title: Vidal Teracam Untuk Ditransfer Dari Barcelona
body:
![IMG_20190805_170243.jpg](https://cdn.steemitimages.com/DQmTX1nh5ZPmHDmeGVHHtu6Jn8qz5cHRHG4piqRVe5MS553/IMG_20190805_170243.jpg) *Image by : CalcioMercato.com* Mantan pelatih Athletic Bilbao Valverde yang saat ini menjadi pelatih di Barcelona dikabarkan akan membuka peluang untuk menjual salah satu gelandang mereka. Menurutnya Barcelona memiliki terlalu banyak gelandang. Dengan demikian Barcelona akan menunggu tim yang akan bertukar permainan di bursa transfer musim ini.   Musim ini, mereka baru saja membawa gelang yang merupakan mantan pemain AjaxAmsterdam. Frenkie de Jong adalah gelandang yang akan menjadi andalan bagi tim Barcelona musim ini. Selain itu, Barcelona juga memiliki galandang muda berusia 19 tahun yang akan bermain di awal musim. Gelandang muda itu adalah Riqui Pug. Dengan demikian jumlah pemain lini tengah Barcelona akan berjumlah 7 pemain.   Penjualan salah satu gelandang mereka dipandang sebagai upaya penggalangan dana untuk memiliki Neymar. Ada dua nama yang terdaftar di bursa transfer, yaitu Ivan Rakitic dan Arturo Vidal.   Dalam hal ini Vidal menjadi pemain yang terancam ditransfer setelah Barcelona datang dengan de Jong dan Puig.
#### [Blog Resource](https://www.ligaolahraga.com/bola/stok-melimpah-barcelona-siap-jual-salah-satu-gelandangnya)
